# AuraBoot CODEOWNERS
#
# These owners are auto-requested as reviewers when a PR touches files
# matching the pattern. They're NOT a permission gate — anyone can still
# merge — but the auto-request means the right people see the review
# request without the contributor having to know who to tag.
#
# Ownership is conservative on day one — most paths land on the @core
# team. Hand off to specialists as the contributor base grows.
#
# IMPORTANT: This file references the team `@AuraBootTeam/core`. The team
# MUST exist on GitHub before this file is committed to a public repo —
# otherwise GitHub silently no-ops the auto-review-request and a "review
# from CODEOWNERS" branch protection rule will block every PR.
#
# Bootstrap sequence (do once before going public):
#   1. gh api -X PUT /orgs/AuraBootTeam/teams/core/repos/AuraBootTeam/auraboot \
#        -f permission=push
#   2. Add at least 2 maintainers to the team:
#        gh api -X PUT /orgs/AuraBootTeam/teams/core/memberships/<user>
#   3. Verify: gh api /orgs/AuraBootTeam/teams/core (must return 200)

# --- Defaults ---
*                                            @AuraBootTeam/core

# --- Licensing & legal (high-stakes; always need maintainer eyes) ---
LICENSE.txt                                  @AuraBootTeam/core
LICENSE-FAQ*.md                              @AuraBootTeam/core
CLA.md                                       @AuraBootTeam/core
NOTICE                                       @AuraBootTeam/core
TELEMETRY.md                                 @AuraBootTeam/core
SECURITY.md                                  @AuraBootTeam/core
CHANGELOG.md                                 @AuraBootTeam/core

# --- CI / release infrastructure (don't accidentally break the build) ---
/.github/                                    @AuraBootTeam/core
/scripts/                                    @AuraBootTeam/core

# --- License signing key (any change here is a security event) ---
/platform/src/main/resources/license/        @AuraBootTeam/core

# --- Demo / launch guardrails ---
/platform/src/main/java/com/auraboot/framework/demo/  @AuraBootTeam/core
